eu.stratosphere.nephele.client

Class JobCancelResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.stratosphere.nephele.client.AbstractJobResult
      • eu.stratosphere.nephele.client.JobCancelResult

  • public final class JobCancelResult
extends AbstractJobResult
    A job cancel result is used to report the result of a job cancel request. It contains a return code and a description. In case of a submission error the description includes an error message.

    This class is thread-safe.

    Author:
    warneke
